## 3. 资产市场页面流程

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph "资产市场"
        START["🏪 市场首页"]
        BROWSE["🔍 资产浏览"]
        DETAIL["📋 资产详情"]
        LINEAGE["🌳 资产谱系"]
        TRENDING["📈 热门排行"]
        PUBLISH["📤 发布资产"]
    end

    START --> BROWSE
    START --> TRENDING
    BROWSE -->|点击资产| DETAIL
    DETAIL -->|查看谱系| LINEAGE
    START --> PUBLISH
    BROWSE --> PUBLISH
```

