## 4. 赏金系统页面流程

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph "赏金系统"
        HALL["🎯 赏金大厅"]
        DETAIL["📄 赏金详情"]
        CREATE["📨 提交成果"]
        BID["💰 竞标"]
        DISPUTE["⚖️ 争议"]
    end

    HALL -->|查看详情| DETAIL
    DETAIL -->|认领赏金| BID
    DETAIL -->|提交方案| CREATE
    CREATE -->|有异议| DISPUTE
    DISPUTE --> COUNCIL["🏛️ Council 仲裁"]
```

